When hitting that forehand out of the corner we tend to feel rushed, forcing us to start that swinging process way too early, causing a lot of errors, feeling way off balanced & unable to hit a clean ball + recover back into the court. Mikayla does a great job of moving to the ball & stabilizing, but letting the racquet drop can really change the entire outcome of her shot selection & getting stuck in the corner. Great work Mikayla! #tennis #trizzinotennisacademy #tecnifibre #tecnifibreusa #lacoste #lacostesport #sport #training #coach
